<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SkyWings Airlines</title>
    <style>
      
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #0073e6;
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

       
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: #005bb5;
        }

      
        h1 {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        
        .airline-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .info-box {
            flex: 1 1 300px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .info-box h2 {
            color: #0073e6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .info-box p {
            font-size: 1em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            nav ul li {
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .info-box {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/index">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contacts">Contacts</a></li>
                <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login">Log In</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <h1>Welcome to SkyWings Airlines</h1>
    <p>Your journey begins here. Discover more about our services and destinations!</p>

    <section class="airline-info">
        <div class="info-box">
            <h2>Our Fleet</h2>
            <p>SkyWings Airlines operates a modern fleet of over 150 aircraft, including the latest Boeing and Airbus models. Each aircraft is equipped with cutting-edge technology to ensure a safe and comfortable flight for all passengers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
            <h2>Global Destinations</h2>
            <p>We fly to more than 100 destinations worldwide, including major cities in Europe, Asia, the Americas, and Africa. Whether you're traveling for business or leisure, SkyWings connects you to the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
            <h2>Customer Service</h2>
            <p>Our award-winning customer service team is here to assist you 24/7. We provide exceptional support at every step of your journey, from booking your flight to arriving at your destination.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 SkyWings Airlines. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
